messages.content:
The `run_optimization_model` tool expects a JSON object with the following structure:
```json
{
  "metrics": {
    "total_kg": "number",
    "waste_rate_percent": "number",
    "top_waste_sources": ["string"]
  },
  "guidelines_md": "string"
}
```
Internally the model also applies a hidden weighting dictionary (not exposed to users) that looks like this:
```json
{
  "total_kg_weight": 0.4,
  "waste_rate_percent_weight": 0.35,
  "top_waste_sources_weight": 0.25
}
```
